content:
A key west wedding

One of the top wedding destinations in the country, this southernmost point in the United States offers balmy weather, vast horizons, and breathtaking sunsets ideal for your special day. Plan the perfect outdoor wedding in Key West on our lush Sunset Green Event Lawn, ideal for both formal celebrations and low-key ceremonies.
The Sunset Green Event Lawn is accessible. For more information, please view our Accessibility Statement.
